#  Conclusion

This analysis demonstrates that successful restaurant expansion requires more than selecting a popular location.

By integrating market competition, customer engagement, pricing strategies, cuisine demand, and digital service adoption, businesses can make informed decisions that reduce risk and improve long-term performance.

The recommendations presented in this document provide a practical framework for leveraging data analytics in restaurant expansion planning.
